text: Jędrzej is an archaic, but still used Polish form of the given name Andrzej (Andrew). ==Notable individuals with the given name Jędrzej== *Jędrzej Śniadecki *Jędrzej Moraczewski *Jędrzej Gruszczyński *Jędrzej Maćkowiak *Jędrzej Giertych *Jędrzej Kitowicz *Jędrzej Jędrych Category:Polish masculine given names
title: Jędrzej
